industry real estateconstruction y sales change  fiscal year ends december  download reports description klil industries ltd klil industries ltd engages in the development design manufacture and sale of aluminum systems for buildings it operates through the following segments profiles and shutters the profiles segment involves manufacturing dyeing and sale of aluminum for the construction industry the shutter segment consists of manufacture and sale of shutter steps aluminum cans and shutter boxes aluminum cans combined with polyurethane foam the company was founded in  and is headquartered in karmiel israel expand key people klil industries ltd board of directors nametitle current board membership tzur daboosh  chairman klil industries ltd arie richtman  chief executive officer  director klil industries ltd diana laban external director klil industries ltd kobi levy  director klil industries ltd golan heights winery ltd michael lazer  external director klil industries ltd neomi enoch  independent director otzar marine industries ltd klil industries ltd keter publishing house ltd expand all executives tzur daboosh chairman arie richtman chief executive officer  director yonatan robinson chief financial officer roy shenkar managerbusiness development diana laban external director kobi levy director saar shuster vice presidentsales menashe david bitton accountant gal amit internal auditor michael lazer external director neomi enoch independent director expand advertisement average growth rates klil industries ltd past five years ending  fiscal year revenue  net income  earnings per share  capital spending  gross margin  cash flow  insider trading klil industries ltd transaction summarytotal insider purchases and sales reported to the sec data not available data not available ownership klil industries ltd mutual funds that own klil name shares held  shares out change in shares  of assets as of date      government pension fund  global the      yelin lapidot menayatit  